DESCRIPTION
    Eulerian Video Magnification to detect heartbeats

USAGE
    python src/evm.py [-h] --video_path VIDEO_PATH [--level LEVEL]
              [--amplification AMPLIFICATION] [--min_frequency MIN_FREQUENCY]
              [--max_frequency MAX_FREQUENCY] --saving_path SAVING_PATH
              [--mode {gaussian,laplacian}]

REFERENCES
    Eulerian Video Magnification for Revealing Subtle Changes in the World (https://people.csail.mit.edu/mrub/evm/)

